'''Sparx Systems Enterprise Architect'''是一款基于[[对象管理组织|OMG]] [[UML|UML]]的可视化模型与设计工具，提供了对软件系统的设计和构建、业务流程建模和基于领域建模的支持，被企业和组织不仅应用于对系统的建模，还用于推进模型在整个应用程序开发周期中实现。

== 概况 ==
UML建模为组织架构各个方面的建模奠定了基础，并为设计和实现新的系统、修改遗留系统提供了方便。UML可以为制定组织或系统架构<ref name="Developing an Enterprise-wide Architecture">{{cite web | url = http://www.sparxsystems.com/press/articles/pdf/IAG_Case_Study.pdf | title = Developing an Enterprise-wide Architecture IAG | author = IAG New Zealand | publisher = [[Sparx_Systems|Sparx Systems]] | accessdate = 2014-03-28 | archive-date = 2013-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130522113934/http://www.sparxsystems.com/press/articles/pdf/IAG_Case_Study.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref>、业务流程重组、{{tsl|en|Business analysis|营业分析}}、面向服务的体系结构、{{tsl|en|Web modeling|模型驱动的网页开发}}<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.cephas.cc/sitecontent/?q=content/enacting-service-oriented-modeling-framework-somf-using-enterprise-architect | title = Enacting the Service Oreinted Modelng Framework | author = Frank Truyen | publisher = Cephas | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120327162257/http://www.cephas.cc/sitecontent/?q=content%2Fenacting-service-oriented-modeling-framework-somf-using-enterprise-architect | archivedate = 2012-03-27 | accessdate = 2017-09-04 }}</ref><ref name="Service Oriented Architecture Roadmap">{{cite web | url = http://community.sparxsystems.com/whitepapers/service-oriented-architecture/iconix-process-service-oriented-architecture-roadmap-soa | author = Doug Rosenberg | title = Service Oriented Architecture Roadmap | publisher = Sparx Systems | accessdate = 2014-03-28 | archive-date = 2012-09-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120908210312/http://community.sparxsystems.com/whitepapers/service-oriented-architecture/iconix-process-service-oriented-architecture-roadmap-soa | dead-url = no }}</ref>、应用程序与数据库设计和再造、嵌入式系统开发<ref name="Embedded Systems using SyML">{{cite web | url = http://www.iconixsw.com/ZIP/Embedded_Systems_SysML_E-book_models.zip | title = Embedded Systems Development using SysML | author = Doug Rosenberg | publisher = Iconix | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120327162237/http://www.iconixsw.com/ZIP/Embedded_Systems_SysML_E-book_models.zip | archivedate = 2012-03-27 | accessdate = 2014-03-28 }}</ref>等方面服务。

从需求、设计、建造、测试到维护阶段，从各阶段项目管理、变更控制工具，到适用于模型驱动开发的内建集成开发环境，Enterprise Architect涵盖了应用程序开发生命周期的核心问题。其用户群覆盖了从小型开发企业、跨国公司、政府机构到国际行业标准机构的程序员、业务分析师到企业架构师。<ref name="Geospatial Standards">{{cite web | url = http://www.sparxsystems.com/downloads/pdf/GeoSciMLEACaseStudy.pdf | title = Geoscience Australia and CSIRO Developing the GeoSciML interoperability standard with Enterprise Architect | author = Dr Simon Cox, Nicholas Ardlie | publisher = Sparx Systems | accessdate = 2014-03-28 | archive-date = 2013-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130522121954/http://www.sparxsystems.com/downloads/pdf/GeoSciMLEACaseStudy.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.sparxsystems.com/downloads/pdf/GeoSciMLEACaseStudy.pdf | title = Modeling for interoperable geospatial Information using the ISO 19100 | author = Pavel Golodoniuc, Dr Simon Cox | publisher = CSIRO | accessdate = 2014-03-28 | archive-date = 2013-05-22 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130522121954/http://www.sparxsystems.com/downloads/pdf/GeoSciMLEACaseStudy.pdf | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Safety Standards">{{cite web  | url=http://www.safetyonline.com/article.mvc/Sparx-Systems-Enterprise-Architect-Supports-0001  | title=Safety Standards Online  | publisher=www.safetyonline.com  | accessdate=2014-03-28  | archive-date=2012-03-25  | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120325191940/http://www.safetyonline.com/article.mvc/Sparx-Systems-Enterprise-Architect-Supports-0001  | dead-url=no  }}</ref>

Sparx Systems从2000年起开始发布Enterprise Architect，最初是为UML 1.1建模的UML建模工具，目前已经支持其他的[[对象管理组织|OMG]] [[UML|UML]]标准，如1.3、2.0、2.1、2.3和2.4.1。

